TO INSTALL:

COPY
------
Copy all the content of QWeb under /share/Qweb/plugmedia/
copy the content of cgi-bin under /home/httpd/cgi-bin/

CHMOD
------
Chmod folder to 0777 /share/Qweb/plugmedia/system/_cache
Chmod folder to 0777 /share/Qweb/plugmedia/system/_compiled
Chmod folder to 0777 /share/Qweb/plugmedia/system/logs
Chmod file to 0777 /share/Qweb/plugmedia/system/config/users.php
Chmod file to 0777 /share/Qweb/plugmedia/system/config/groups.php
Chmod file to 0777 /share/Qweb/plugmedia/system/config/plugmedia_admin.php

Chmod file to 0755 /home/httpd/cgi-bin/cgi_auth.cgi


MODIFY
-------
Modify the file /share/Qweb/plugmedia/system/config/config.php according to your prefs
$config['base_url']	= "http://IP_OR_DDNS/plugmedia/";

CHECK
------
Go to http://IP_OR_DDNS/plugmedia/check.php (just last 2 lines must be red)